==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enmesh
<hw>En*mesh"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>mesh</ets>. Cf. <er>Inmesh</er>.]</ety> <def>To
catch or entangle in, or as in, meshes.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My doubts <qex>enmesh</qex> me if I try.</q>
<rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enmew</ent>⟦br⟧
